<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-hero-image-wrap">
      <%= image_tag "dashboard-ai-tools.jpg", alt: "AI-powered sourcing tools for sports and fitness – coming soon", class: "page-hero-image" %>
    </div>
    <h1 class="section__title mt-0">AI-powered sourcing tools</h1>
    <p class="section__subtitle">We’re building intelligence and automation to help global buyers discover the best sourcing opportunities. These tools are coming soon to the platform.</p>

    <div class="tools-coming-badge">
      <span>Coming soon</span>
    </div>

    <div class="tools-grid">
      <div class="tool-card tool-card--coming">
        <h3 class="tool-card__title">AI Supplier Match</h3>
        <p class="tool-card__desc">Match your product and volume requirements with the best-fit Indian sports and fitness manufacturers. Reduce sourcing time and find verified suppliers that meet your MOQ and certification needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card tool-card--coming">
        <h3 class="tool-card__title">AI Price Benchmarking</h3>
        <p class="tool-card__desc">Compare quotes and market rates for gym equipment, sports gear, and fitness products. Make informed decisions with data-driven pricing insights.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card tool-card--coming">
        <h3 class="tool-card__title">Export Market Demand Analyzer</h3>
        <p class="tool-card__desc">See which sports and fitness products are in demand by region and channel. Validate product opportunity before you source.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card tool-card--coming">
        <h3 class="tool-card__title">Product Opportunity Finder</h3>
        <p class="tool-card__desc">Discover high-opportunity products for your market. Identify gaps and emerging demand in fitness, gym, and sports categories.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="section__subtitle" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Our long-term vision is to power global trade through data and AI—starting with sports and fitness, then expanding across industries.</p>
    <p class="text-center" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <%= link_to "Back to platform", root_path, class: "btn btn--secondary" %>
      <%= link_to "Find manufacturers now", products_path, class: "btn btn--primary" %>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
